ual report of the board to Congress. See "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t12/s1437/b"},"text":"section 1437(b) of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1950—Act ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1950-06-27"},"text":"June 27, 1950","children":[],"tail":", struck out “twice” before “annually”."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
